        <!-- Introduction Section -->
        <section id="introduction" class="mb-16" data-aos="fade-up">
            <h2 class="section-title">1. Introduction</h2>
            <div class="prose mt-4 space-y-4">
                <p><strong>Problem:</strong> Planning a trip is often a time-consuming and fragmented process. Travelers spend hours searching multiple websites for flights, hotels, and activities, struggling to piece together a coherent and feasible itinerary. They lack a centralized, intelligent tool that can understand their unique preferences and generate a personalized plan instantly.</p>
                <p><strong>Solution:</strong> The AI Travel Planner is a web-based application that acts as a smart travel assistant. By using a powerful generative AI model, it transforms simple, natural language requests into detailed, structured, and enriched travel itineraries. The goal is to drastically reduce planning time, eliminate friction, and inspire users with creative and personalized travel ideas.</p>
                <p><strong>Goals:</strong></p>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                    <li>To provide a seamless, conversational interface for trip planning.</li>
                    <li>To generate high-quality, personalized itineraries in seconds.</li>
                    <li>To enrich travel plans with real-world data, making them more actionable.</li>
                    <li>To become the go-to starting point for any traveler's planning journey.</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- User Personas Section -->
        <section id="personas" class="mb-16">
