                            <p><strong>Needs:</strong></p>
                            <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                                <li>Clear cost estimates for activities.</li>
                                <li>Suggestions for budget-friendly accommodation and food.</li>
                                <li>An easy way to see if her plan is too rushed.</li>
                            </ul>
